title: The Eyes
description: One night, an exhausted Finn and Jake are creeped out by an odd-looking horse that mysteriously appears outside the treehouse and keeps them awake.  They try everything they can think of to get rid of the freaky horse, but nothing seems to work.  What does it want?  And why won't it just leave them alone?
